@startuml
skinparam defaultFontName "DejaVu Sans"
skinparam defaultFontSize 15
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign left
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
hide footbox

title Direct POST /api/opportunities/search
autonumber 1 "<b>[00]"

actor "Prototype or test caller" as Caller
participant "Controller" as API
participant "Opportunity engine\nand scoring pipeline" as Engine

note over Caller, Engine
  The browser does not use this ordinary-mode path.
  It accepts only the Prague fixture and fixture weather;
  no live geocoding or weather provider is called.
end note

Caller -> API: POST direct scoring JSON
API -> API: Parse and validate the request body

alt Malformed, incomplete, or invalid fields
  API --> Caller: 400 invalid_request
else Valid request shape
  API -> Engine: Evaluate prototype request
  alt Unsupported fixture or out-of-range value
    Engine --> API: Invalid request
    API --> Caller: 400 invalid_request
  else Valid Prague request
    Engine -> Engine: Generate and score with caller horizon, ceiling, and limit
    Engine --> API: Opportunity result
    API --> Caller: 200 opportunity result
  end
end

@enduml
